{"tid":781522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男熟客疑酒吧撩女 一講錢就遭爆樽","createTime":"2018-08-16T03:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T15:33:03.000Z","uid":5919,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1fec1f06bfe3af990440e5916d45bf452db36ca6","tid":781522,"uid":5919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:05:04.000Z","msg":"紅磡馬頭圍道一間酒吧，清晨5時，姓莫(37歲)男熟客前來光顧，其間與一名女酒客搭訕，該名女酒客當時與另外兩名朋友同行，莫要求與女酒客合照被拒，其間又談到借錢問題，兩人話不投機，女酒客大怒，手執一個酒樽向莫頭部連扑三下，糾纏間他被抓傷左手。<br />\n<br />\n肇事女酒客偕友人乘亂搭小巴逃去，莫報警求助，警方接報到場，莫頭腫手傷送院治理。他到達醫院情緒激動指駡記者，揚言拆菲林，並在急症室向警員投訴，由警員勸止。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/110419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F110419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=34b883d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味拆菲林<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413978fe05f1c781270b5685d2dde911d6692b0e","tid":781522,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"係咪唔小心問咗 how much?"},{"pid":"53e44bdf2dcd3df8f4bd59215cd0220035484907","tid":781522,"uid":35382,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"個樣好似林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5a956cd6ffa34b61f2ec0fcbd0cf5816567c62","tid":781522,"uid":5919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"413978fe05f1c781270b5685d2dde911d6692b0e","tid":781522,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"係咪唔小心問咗 how much?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"冇理解錯應該問條女借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42f1c57296d928cb1739857673c5a79c3e078ab","tid":781522,"uid":